Calculations accounting for nuclear deformation in MSD nicely reproduce the data in the direct continuum region while the "spherical" calculations underpredict the same data. It should be stressed that, except for adjustment of dynamic deformations used in the coupled-channel calculations and the fission input, these results were obtained without any adjustment of the MSD part of the calculations. In the IAEA evaluation for 
