 interaction diagrams is summed exactly. Thus, an essential contribution to the intrinsic correlations is treated explicitly. In the notation of Section 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sec: MSD"

\end_inset

 they are part of 
\begin_inset Formula $H_{0}^{intr}$
\end_inset

. Thus, the 
\begin_inset Formula $ph-$
\end_inset

classes are built from correlated basis states. This justifies also the 
\shape italic
ansatz
\shape default
 of Eq. 
