\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
after ""
key "Wal,BM,LW92,SLW,RegT"

\end_inset

. The approach describes at the same time the large amount of weakly excited background states and the strongly excited giant resonances 
\begin_inset Formula $(GR)$
\end_inset

