\begin_inset Formula $T_{A}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $T_{B}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $T_{C}$
\end_inset

), for direct transmission (
\begin_inset Formula $T_{dir}$
