EMPIRE can be executed either with the included Graphical User Interface (GUI), or from the command-line using scripts. The Graphic User Interface mode is the most convenient, and is recommended if a Tcl/Tk interpreter is available. Where the Tcl/Tk interpreter is not available, the user is advised to use the script mode. 
