\begin_layout Standard

Consideration and observation of the following remarks will help to avoid problems when running the EMPIRE code:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

Each modification of the EMPIRE input file (*.
\emph on
inp
\emph default
) that involves a change of projectile, target, or the number of emitted particles must be followed by the execution of the 
\emph on
clean
\emph default
